items.title: Surprise Guest
items.description:
scott5024 posted a photo:

As I was sitting on the rocks on top of a mountain, waiting to photograph the usual mountain subjects, a surprise guest wanders in. One of the last critters I expected to see was a porcupine high above the tree line.
Denali National Park, AK
